# TFS_CHAIN · GITIGNORE
# MINES. VENTURE, LLC · IAMBIGRAPPER1 · ALL RIGHTS MINES.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# What stays OUT of the public repo:
#   - Rust build artifacts (multi-GB, regenerable)
#   - IDE / editor junk
#   - Environment secrets
#   - Cryptographic key material (NEVER commit keys)
#   - Running chain state (RocksDB data)
#   - OS-specific files
#
# What stays IN:
#   - All .rs source files
#   - Cargo.toml (locked deps)
#   - Cargo.lock (for reproducible builds of the binary)
#   - Documentation, tests, scrolls
#
# Remember: the CODE is public. The KEYS are sovereign. Never confuse them.

# ─── Rust build artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# ─── Cryptographic key material · NEVER COMMIT ──────────────────────
*.key
*.pem
*.priv
*.secret
*.seed
keys/
keystore/
/validator-keys/
president-mines.key
genesis-keypair.json

# ─── Environment + secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.env.local
secrets/
*.secrets

# ─── Chain state (regenerable, huge, contains validator data) ──────
data/
chaindata/
db/
/blocks/
*.rocksdb
*.sst
*.log

# ─── IDE / editor ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# ─── OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Dragon Run artifacts (working notes, not committed) ────────────
/dragon-runs/scratch/
*.dragonrun.tmp
